         card (z:30) so a tap always reaches it. The expanded panel
         below uses the same stacking context. */
      z-index: 40;
      animation: core-search-trigger-pulse 3.4s ease-in-out infinite;
      transition:
        transform 220ms cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1),
